## ðŸ” 2.3 Mitigation Techniques

- **Security Patches** â€“ Apply updates regularly
- **User Awareness Training** â€“ Combat phishing & SE
- **Firewall Rules** â€“ Block known bad traffic
- **Access Controls** â€“ Least privilege model
- **Network Segmentation** â€“ Limit attack scope
- **Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA)** â€“ Defends against credential theft
- **Endpoint Protection** â€“ AV/EDR for malware detection

